  title      = {Condition, length–weight and length–length relationships of the {Asian} striped catfish \textit{{Mystus} vittatus} ({Bloch}, 1794) ({Siluriformes}: {Bagridae}) in the {Mathabhanga} {River}, southwestern {Bangladesh}},
